originalText.text: I've seen Yokasta 10 times, spanning nearly the past 2 years. I am grateful to have met her and found her practice. I go for holistic massage therapy. I originally started going for back pain but now I just go for general health maintenance - both physical and mental! I always feel calmer and lighter after leaving her space. Besides her obvious massage skills and down to earth attitude, what is special about Yokasta is how she values me as a client and keeps me in mind even when I'm not there. She'll sometimes send me resources on topics we discussed or if something comes across her radar that she thinks might benefit me. I highly recommend going to Yokasta for your massage needs.

originalText.text: I booked a session for myself and my partner. We both loved our experience. The smells, sounds and overall flow of the session created a soothing atmosphere. Yokasta has a kindness and grace that comforts and helps you be present to the healing. Both my partner and I felt so much better afterward. We highly recommend Kasa.
